    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't know if there's anything left to build on though. when you look at a house that's been burnt to the ground, you don't really talk about \"building\" on the ashes. you just see what's gone. it feels like there's no point in trying to rebuild a person that doesn't exist anymore. i'm just tired of being this... this empty thing.",
